<template>
  <!-- Seu conteúdo Vue aqui -->
</template>

<script>
import Typebot from 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@typebot.io/js@0.2.22/dist/web.js';

export default {
  mounted() {
    const script = document.createElement('script');
    script.type = 'module';
    script.src = 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@typebot.io/js@0.2.22/dist/web.js';
    script.onload = () => {
      Typebot.initPopup({
        typebot: "diagnostico-horas",
        apiHost: "https://tbchat.dourasoft.com.br",
        autoShowDelay: 0,
      });
    };
    document.body.appendChild(script);
  }
}
</script>
